Cards.EffectString: RoundEnd <[Self,HarvestIncome,-1]><{Self,HarvestIncome,Equal,0}[CreateItemAround(黑兔兔(灾年);1)][Self,HarvestIncome,2]> # RoundBegin <{Global,Tally(Around'(Name'Is'三只黑兔兔(灾年))),Bigger,1}[DestroyItem(RandomRange(Filter(Around'(Name'Is'三只黑兔兔(灾年))) : 2))][Transfer(Self;星夜兔兔(灾年))]>

Cards.Name: 星夜兔兔(灾年)
Cards.EffectDescription: 回合结束：+10金币

Cards.Name: 点金藤(灾年)
Cards.EffectDescription: 收成：+3{HarvestIncome}金币；每打出1张衍生物+1生长值
